          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1697453789233-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut your <strong>cucumber</strong> in half lengthways and scrape out the inner seeds with a teaspoon, throw the watery seeds away, then slice finely</p><p>Add the <strong>sliced cucumber</strong> to a small bowl with your <strong>rice vinegar </strong>and a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Stir everything together and set aside – this is your<strong> quick-pickled cucumber</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1697453785400-x200.jpg",
