            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>sriracha </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) and <strong>mayo</strong> in a bowl – this is your <strong>sriracha mayo</strong></p><p>Rinse your <strong>blanched edamame beans</strong> under <strong>cold running water</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>blanched edamame beans</strong> to a bowl with <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>sriracha mayo </strong>(save the rest for garnish!) and a good grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>edamame salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1697453772783-x200.jpg",
